[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     14[0m:[38;5;10m[49m This is one of the strongest recipes in Chapter 8. The problem statement is emotionally compelling and clinically grounded, the technology section teaches SDOH NLP from first principles with honest performance expectations, and the architecture pattern is appropriate for the stated scale. The recipe correctly frames system output as "reviewed = false" by default, requiring human validation before acting on extractions. The Gravity Project taxonomy alignment and ICD-10 Z-code normalization demonstrate genuine domain expertise. No CRITICAL findings. One HIGH finding (VPC endpoint claim for Comprehend Medical that likely cannot be fulfilled). Three MEDIUM findings for architectural completeness. The recipe is publishable with the HIGH item addressed.
